{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Something I could have done in two days, I worked on for three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And, and I had enough to eat with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that time, in my-- I described it in more details in my book.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I had time to think, and I was thinking of what would I do with after the war and how would I hug and kiss and never quarrel again if I would meet my mother and sister again.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Or take a machine gun to kill Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Kill, kill, kill Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was actually shooting in my mind, in my semi-dreams, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And suddenly I saw faces I knew when I stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I also saw children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I thought, well, children have been killed by the Germans as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I got-- carried on shooting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But even in my sort of dream or semi-dream, I aimed higher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The awakening, of course, was that I was like every awakening, you're back where you were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Shortly after that, one day, the Russians had made another offensive, and we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After another march-- not death march.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The death march came at the very end, but it really probably had started then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We came to another either nearby camp or station, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it's-- the memories go vague sometimes in timing and small details.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was a train we had to get onto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I was looking out, and I could see Max Spira or Adolf Konig again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "After all, these were people of, you know, probably prepare themselves with more food and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
